Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives - Season 23, Episode 9




Finger Lickin' Food

This trip, Guy Fieri is eating up grub that doesn't require a knife and fork! In Atlanta, a funky old house turned brew pub cookin' up cheddarwurst corn dogs along with a knockout pastrami sandwich. In Minneapolis, an English-Filipino mashup serving the bomb bahn mi and bacon onion dip. Then, in Woods Hole, Mass., a seafood spot dishing out mussels and lobster-stuffed cod.




Original Air Date: 02-Oct-2015
